  m_text: "LVL_2: here i want more trees to start appearing, i want trees to block
    some of the street, obstructing the players view as they walk past (scrolling
    trees, like a BG but its an overlay in front of the scene) \nI want more rural
    view with visual indicators of the city's plans on branching out, beyond the
    forest area. (Signs of planned builds etc.) \nI want there to be powerplants
    and other industrial stuff in the distance of the BG."
